		<div class="post" id="431">
		
			<h2><a href="http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/blog/2010/top-50-fashion-books-of-all-time/">Top 50 Fashion Books of All Time</a></h2>

			<div class='bookmarkify'><a name='bookmarkify'></a><div class='linkbuttons'><a href='http://del.icio.us/post?url=http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/blog/2010/top-50-fashion-books-of-all-time/&amp;title=Top 50 Fashion Books of All Time' title='Save to del.icio.us' onclick='target="_blank";' rel='nofollow'><img src='http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/wp-content/plugins/bookmarkify/delicious.png' style='width:16px; height:16px;' alt='[del.icio.us] ' /></a> <a href='http://digg.com/submit?phase=2&amp;url=http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/blog/2010/top-50-fashion-books-of-all-time/&amp;title=Top 50 Fashion Books of All Time' title='Digg It!' onclick='target="_blank";' rel='nofollow'><img src='http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/wp-content/plugins/bookmarkify/digg.png' style='width:16px; height:16px;' alt='[Digg] ' /></a> <a href='http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/blog/2010/top-50-fashion-books-of-all-time/' title='Save to Facebook' onclick='target="_blank";' rel='nofollow'><img src='http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/wp-content/plugins/bookmarkify/facebook.png' style='width:16px; height:16px;' alt='[Facebook] ' /></a> <a href='http://www.mixx.com/submit?page_url=http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/blog/2010/top-50-fashion-books-of-all-time/' title='Save to Mixx' onclick='target="_blank";' rel='nofollow'><img src='http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/wp-content/plugins/bookmarkify/mixx.png' style='width:16px; height:16px;' alt='[Mixx] ' /></a> <a href='http://reddit.com/submit?url=http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/blog/2010/top-50-fashion-books-of-all-time/&amp;title=Top 50 Fashion Books of All Time' title='Reddit' onclick='target="_blank";' rel='nofollow'><img src='http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/wp-content/plugins/bookmarkify/reddit.png' style='width:16px; height:16px;' alt='[Reddit] ' /></a> <a href='http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http://www.bachelorsdegreeonline.com/blog/2010/top-50-fashion-books-of-a